snippet.title: AMENTI™ - Ancient Egypt Horror Game | Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
AMENTI™
Wishlist Now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3292260/Amenti/

This horror game take you into the darkside of ancient Egypt, To uncover the connection between aliens and the Egyptians, you must explore the tomb of Egypt’s most mysterious pharaohs, Local legends warn that entering this tomb triggers terrifying events and it seems these legends may be true

@darkphobiagames
